ST. VINCENT de PAUL ORLANDO in Action
It’s easy for SVDP Orlando Conferences to provide a Voucher to a Neighbor in Need!
St. Vincent de Paul Orlando Thrift Stores work with SVDP Conferences & non-profits to provide Furniture, Appliances and Clothing Vouchers to our neighbors in need across Central Florida.
St. Vincent de Paul Orlando Thrift Stores have filled 613 Clothing Vouchers and 96 Conference Furniture and Appliance Vouchers totaling $65,000 this year.
